525
01:02:18,600 --> 01:02:21,239
Yeah, he's turned rogue
and can't be controlled, is that it?

526
01:02:33,680 --> 01:02:36,319
Excusez-moi.
Je cherche la vieille maison de Van Gogh.

527
01:02:36,440 --> 01:02:39,398
