- Oh, English.

528
01:02:39,480 --> 01:02:41,311
Sorry. Such a fool.

529
01:02:41,440 --> 01:02:43,237
I was looking for Van Gogh's old house.

530
01:02:43,320 --> 01:02:47,552
So what could have been conducted
in a collegial atmosphere

531
01:02:47,680 --> 01:02:49,671
